data.revised_prompt: Envision a robot with a shiny blue metallic body. The robot is designed with futuristic aesthetics, equipped with LED eyes that emit a vibrant glitched effect. It is sitting comfortably at a spacious desk in a high-tech lab. In its flexible mechanical hands, it's holding a bright LED screen that displays a YAML file with complex strings of code. The lab around the robot is filled with various machinery and spare parts, illuminated by a soft glow from the neon lights around. All of these details create a captivating scene of a robot immersed in learning and understanding the intricacies of YAML files.
